  "texts": [
    "Emotional Intelligence in Interactions Empathy plays a crucial role in addressing customer frustrations.",
    "While ChatGPT focuses on understanding the factual content of interactions, Gemini analyzes sentiment and emotional cues within customer communications.",
    "This enables Gemini to guide ChatGPT's responses toward a more empathetic tone and suggest de-escalation tactics when necessary.",
    "By combining factual understanding with emotional intelligence, this approach demonstrates a deeper level of care and a commitment to resolving emotionally charged situations.",
    "Enhanced Self-Service and Automation ChatGPT enhances self-service portals by providing answers to common questions, guiding users through processes, and directing them to relevant resources [38,41]."
